    "description": "Tuck into this chana masala-inspired fibre fix. You'll cook off chickpeas, onion, tomato and spices until tender. Then, simmer your five bean medley until soft in a rich curry sauce and top with coconut. Serve up with fluffy naan and enjoy. A source of fibre with at least a third of your recommended daily intake.",
